<h1>Pick Your Own Organic Produce</h1>
<p>Experience the joy of hand-picking your own fresh organic fruits and vegetables directly from our farm! It's 
    a fun and sustainable way to enjoy nature and take home the freshest produce possible.</p>

<h2>What You Can Pick</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Strawberries (May - June)</li>
    <li>Blueberries (June - July)</li>
    <li>Tomatoes (July - September)</li>
    <li>Apples (September - October)</li>
    <li>Pumpkins (October)</li>
</ul>

<h2>Plan Your Visit</h2>
<p>Our farm is open for picking during the following hours:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Monday - Friday: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</li>
    <li>Saturday - Sunday: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
</ul>
<p>Be sure to bring your own containers, or you can purchase eco-friendly bags at our farm store.</p>

